Privacy Policy


Lupi Game Studio developed the "Gullbird" application as an ad-supported application. This application is provided free of charge and must be used as is.

This privacy policy is used to inform you about the policies for the collection, use and
disclosure of personal information if someone decides to use this service.


1. Overview

The application uses advertising to generate revenue. The application uses third-party advertising libraries that can collect and share personal information with third parties
parties.

Links to privacy policies of third-party service providers used in the app

AdMob https://support.google.com/admob/answer/6128543


2.) Sharing your information

The developer will share personal information with third parties only in the ways that are
described in this privacy statement.

Your personal information may be disclosed:
* As required by law, such as to comply with a subpoena or similar legal process.
* To any other third party with their prior consent to do so.


3. What information is collected and why

3.1 AdMob

AdMob, is Google’s mobile app advertising platform designed specifically for apps
developers. To understand Google’s use of data, please refer to Google’s partner policy.

Personal data:
* Online identifiers, including cookie identifiers
* IP addresses
* Device identifiers
* Customer identifiers
* unique device identifiers for advertising (Google Advertiser ID or IDFA, for example)
* Usage data.

Retention:
Google anonymizes registration data by removing part of the IP address (after 9 months) and
cookie information (after 18 months)

Online resources:
* Privacy policy https://www.google.com/policies/technologies/ads/
* Disable https://www.google.com/settings/ads
* Service information https://privacy.google.com/businesses/adsservices/
* Partner policy https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites
* Ad technology providers https://support.google.com/admob/answer/9012903



4. Security
We strive to keep your information secure.
But remember that no method of transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% safe and reliable, and I cannot guarantee your absolute security.


5. Links to other sites

This service may contain links to other sites. If you click on a third party link, you
will be directed to that site. Please note that these external sites are not operated by me.
Therefore, I strongly recommend that you review the Privacy Policy of those sites. I have
no control and no responsibility for the content, privacy policies or
practices of any third party websites or services.


6. Children's privacy

These services are not directed at anyone under the age of 16.
personally identifiable information for children under 16. In case, I find out that
a child under 16 has provided me with personal information, I delete it immediately
information. If you are a parent or guardian and know that your child has
provided personal information, please contact me so that I can do the necessary
actions.

7. Distribution

The only official distribution channel for this application are:
* Google Play Store https://play.google.com/

Any other mode of distribution is not official and is therefore not maintained by the developer.
This privacy policy is only valid for distribution on an official channel.


8. Changes to this Privacy Policy

This policy may be updated from time to time.


